cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.IT, cs.SI, cs.DS

This paper deals with the approximation of neural networks and rational functions, which is a topic closely related to machine learning and optimization. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.IT (Information Theory). The paper also involves mathematical analysis and complexity theory, which could place it in cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) or cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
